				<h3 class="rich_media_title" id="activity-name">第六空间湖州商场携手交通银行为200＋品牌“金融赋能”！</h3>
				<div id="meta_content" class="rich_media_meta_list">
					<span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_nickname" id="profileBt">
						<a href="javascript:void(0);" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight weui-wa-hotarea" id="js_name"> 湖州第六空间国际家居 </a>
					</span>
